## Theme — TruthSeal Neon v1.3 (dark, low-glare, night-safe)
Use these CSS variables exactly:
```css
:root{
  --bg:#06121f;            /* deep navy/black-blue */
  --panel:#0b1e34;         /* card background */
  --ink:#e6f1ff;           /* soft white-blue text */
  --muted:#9bb3c7;         /* secondary text */
  --line:rgba(123,211,255,.18);
  --chip:rgba(123,211,255,.14);
  --link:#9dd7ff;          /* LIGHT BLUE (preferred) */
  --accent:#5ef0b5;        /* NEON GREEN (preferred) */
  --accent-2:#63a1ff;      /* cyan-blue accent */
  --card:#0f1820;
}
@media print{
  body{background:#fff;color:#000}
  header,.toolbar{display:none}
  a{color:#000;text-decoration:none}
}
